## Follow-up Questions

### ✓ Follow-up: Filter Results
POST @baseUrl/api/dashboard/{dashboard_id}/follow-up
Content-Type: @contentType

{
  "message": "Now filter this to only show East Coast sales"
}

---

### ✓ Follow-up: Focus on Top Products
POST @baseUrl/api/dashboard/{dashboard_id}/follow-up
Content-Type: @contentType

{
  "message": "Show me only the top 3 products"
}

---

### ✓ Follow-up: Add Another Dimension
POST @baseUrl/api/dashboard/{dashboard_id}/follow-up
Content-Type: @contentType

{
  "message": "Break this down by salesperson"
}

---

### ✓ Follow-up: Time Period Change
POST @baseUrl/api/dashboard/{dashboard_id}/follow-up
Content-Type: @contentType

{
  "message": "Look at just February data"
}

---

## Raw Query Execution

### ✓ Execute Simple SELECT
POST @baseUrl/api/query/execute?query_text=SELECT%20*%20FROM%20sales%20LIMIT%2010

---

### ✓ Execute Aggregation Query
POST @baseUrl/api/query/execute?query_text=SELECT%20region,%20SUM(revenue)%20FROM%20sales%20GROUP%20BY%20region

---

### ✓ Execute with WHERE Clause
POST @baseUrl/api/query/execute?query_text=SELECT%20*%20FROM%20sales%20WHERE%20region=%27North%27%20LIMIT%2010

---

